# Regenerable forge artifacts — excluded from the registry commit.
# Recreate per-project with setup_poc.sh + `forge build`.
out/
cache/
broadcast/
.run.lock

# Per-POC lib/ contents are NOT committed, EXCEPT the forge-std symlink that each POC
# needs to resolve to _shared/forge-std. We force-add those symlinks; everything else
# under <poc>/lib/ (if any) is ignored.
lib/*
!lib/forge-std

# Single committed forge-std copy lives under _shared/forge-std (tracked in full).
# (the lib/ ignore above is per-poc; _shared/forge-std is not under a <poc>/lib.)

# Test-run output (regenerated)
_shared/results/

# macOS
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store

# Editor / OS cruft
*.swp
*~
Thumbs.db

# Keep the valuable products: anvil_state.json, output.txt, *.md, sources/,
# foundry.toml, test/, interface.sol, _shared/ tooling — all committed.
